      "message": "[Major] Line 1323: The fallback is applied to every transfer, but it is intended for sent/outgoing files. For incoming transfers, a local file with the same display name and size in the conversation directory could incorrectly mark the transfer as finished, hiding the download button even though this specific fileId was never downloaded. Gate the fallback on isOutgoing so it only fixes the stale daemon-info case for sent files.\n\n```suggestion\n                    if (!isComplete \u0026\u0026 isOutgoing \u0026\u0026 !fileId.isNullOrEmpty()) {\n```",
